channel.title: My command generator v1! (and v2 now)
channel.description:
This is my command generator v1 (v2 now)!!!! I'm new to this so please keep the flaming a bit low, and give some feedback/suggestions. :D
v3 will have: Enable everybody (with its own functions) - - -
well, here it is: v1: [IMG]http://i41.tinypic.com/23u8r44.jpg[/img] v2 (added teleport, emote and gfx): [IMG]http://i42.tinypic.com/5mzrk5.jpg[/img]
Credits: Davidi2 (for helping me out with a couple of things) Google (for guides :P) And myself! ;D (for making this program!)
Download coming soon, if the comments are good and if I know how to make the source be protected :D If somebody knows how, please tell me!!
